Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別坐在角落裡 來這邊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:24.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下海會被海蛇吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:29.46,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:30.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居然無視我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:37.79,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,中世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.53,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1075,1000)}                   Danes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:41.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在丹麥的丹麥人當中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:45.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有一群人成為海盜 以掠奪為生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.94,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1095,1000)}                Vikings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.46,0:00:46.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他們被稱作維京人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:54.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對他們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:56.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,豐饒廣闊的英格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:58.98,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是他們的嚮往之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:04.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,9世紀初 維京人開始入侵英格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:08.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一部分人移居到英格蘭北部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:10.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,勢力範圍不斷擴張
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.73,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 公元1002年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:18.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,英格蘭軍襲擊了移居的維京人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:21.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,作為對這一事件的報復行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:25.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丹麥軍開始向英格蘭派兵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,發起了正式的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:33.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨著這場政局變動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:39.31,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,維京人在這次以擊潰英格蘭軍為目標的征服戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.54,0:01:41.37,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,發揮了重要作用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:21.88,Vinland-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1250,610)\blur7\pos(332,940)}#06 旅途開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別休息 手動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.02,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我這不是在划嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來真是一場大戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 到這一帶就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,停船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.20,Vinland-picture-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,910)}{\blur2\fad(504,510)}                  Gainsborough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.20,Vinland-picture,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(503,510)\pos(970,960)}英格蘭中部     根斯堡周邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.91,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：根斯堡，位於英格蘭中部今林肯郡以內的城鎮。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 真難走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:54.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,氣味果然也很重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:23.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人不是正規軍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:24.89,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,像是跟我們一樣的海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:27.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是被丹麥軍僱傭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被丹麥軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.00,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,維京人在幫丹麥軍打仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:36.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟丹麥軍開始在各地和英格蘭軍起衝突了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:40.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,維京人也是很出色的戰爭工具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:45.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,據說丹麥王遲早也要親征英格蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,多少年後開始倒是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:49.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這應該就是在做準備工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要在國王登陸之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把礙事的傢伙都收拾掉麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,只要給他們幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就能得到很多酬金
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲子真多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:14.64,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,總比挨凍要好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:17.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們得趁這時機好好賺一筆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 這個提議不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:35.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 此處領主麾下的英格蘭軍是挺棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:37.59,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的兵力有100人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:41.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,直說了 戰鬥力也比你們強
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.43,0:05:44.74,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,區區海盜 口氣倒挺大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不都是丹麥人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別把我們和你們相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你們幾年後就會正式攻過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:06.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼越早動手越好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:09.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你們又不會出現傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,7磅金子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:17.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,領主儲藏的全部財寶和食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:19.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,以及所有女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,5磅 其他隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:29.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼定了 交涉成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.99,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 他們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在談工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.54,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,談妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.82,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就先好好吃一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.76,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼明天再派使者找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:48.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,具體怎麼打就交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你們可別跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們沒有退路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是敢耍什麼花招…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.19,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:12.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.51,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我屁股中箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好當作飯後運動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:26.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,開幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.10,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,反殺他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,放箭 放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:39.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰場上立功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:55.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:58.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就給予獎勵 和你決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,立…立功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:09.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.97,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是海盜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要怨就怨你的丹麥人血脈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:41.83,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰場上弱者最先死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:55.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.69,0:10:54.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,變得有模有樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.88,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾芬 你去偵查下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.11,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子 你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:50.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,把他壓住 我來把他砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:17.91,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:19.24,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:40.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊 別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:06.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說現在的國王是不是傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:09.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 這種事情小聲點說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.75,Vinland-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(935,1000)}             Edgar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,上上任的埃德加國王就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:12.75,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：“和平者”埃德加，英格蘭國王（959-975年在位）,\N在位期間與丹麥人維持和平關係，並加強維繫國內統治。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,能與丹麥人和平相處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:21.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是位偉大的基督徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.87,Vinland-tips - pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,0)}             Æthelred II\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在的埃塞爾雷德國王卻糟蹋了這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.87,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(10,25)}註：“決策無方者”埃塞爾雷德二世，下令屠殺丹麥移民，致使丹麥軍隊入侵英格蘭。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:31.12,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要屠殺國內的丹麥移民
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.21,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不惹對方生氣才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:39.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 別在外面說這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.41,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是傳到軍隊士兵的耳朵裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.39,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:48.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.39,Vinland-picture,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,850)}{\blur2\fad(509,510)}公元1008年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.39,Vinland-picture,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,900)}{\blur2\fad(509,510)}東盎格利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.39,Vinland-picture,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(780,900)}{\blur2\fad(509,510)}英格蘭東部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:55.39,Vinland-picture-pronunciation,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,850)}{\blur2\fad(509,510)}East Anglia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:55.02,Vinland-tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：東盎格利亞，原為英國七國時代裡的其中一個盎格魯-撒克遜王國，\N領土位於英格蘭東南部，後來併入英格蘭王國。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:29.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好現在要煮晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.13,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.84,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的衣服已經拿去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.81,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,曬乾之前先穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.38,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,短劍也放在那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:46.72,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服可能有點大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.77,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子的衣服只有這件了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:54.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,餓著肚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是相當餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡人怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:21.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 我就說語言不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.40,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是丹麥人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,無論他是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是對受傷倒下的小孩放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.08,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,主耶穌是不會寬恕我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.18,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,丹麥人是英格蘭的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:42.28,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,爸被去服兵役也是因為丹麥人攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.69,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,男人之間的爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人小孩沒必要跟著摻和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.14,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:07.22,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子頭上全是跳蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.03,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別撓了 會跑進飯菜裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:21.04,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 舒服多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 男孩子都邋裡邋遢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我家小兒子也經常把頭髮弄得亂糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.94,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,每次我都會幫他梳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過前年因為感冒惡化死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:46.56,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的語言我聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:52.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是英格蘭人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:01.32,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 果然還是會說話的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:17.07,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在 請問什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:20.68,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有丹麥人的斥候潛入到這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:22.75,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有見到可疑的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.05,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.16,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,海盜小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.29,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別小瞧那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:33.33,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他殺了領主閣下的兩名正規軍士兵 手法嫻熟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:35.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有箭傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.60,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,女人 那是你的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:52.20,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.43,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我小兒子約翰 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.65,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,正好跟這個孩子差不多身高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.34,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了就必須向我們通報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己在幹什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.30,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是海盜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.63,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還是個小孩 就已經殺死兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:23.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還要掩護他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.87,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩一般不會去做海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.15,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有什麼緣由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:33.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,有緣由又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.86,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,問題關鍵不在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.01,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子可無法代替約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,我去趟軍隊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:02.52,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快...快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:06.53,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.35,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,托爾芬的信號呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該差不多是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:32.92,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:34.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.47,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,海邊的小屋著火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:48.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,男人們集合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.25,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.67,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,拿水桶來 水桶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.93,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然矇混過去了 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.48,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.23,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.45,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:43.09,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.26,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他殺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.80,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你快逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.62,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,特地用英格蘭語說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:07.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,他來這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:09.71,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:10.85,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃到森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.49,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,離海越遠越好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.55,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點 那幫人就要...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:24.17,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:35.90,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:37.95,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:39.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,別管火災了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.78,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:46.58,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,維京人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:58.66,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮 托爾芬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:02.06,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,這村子比預想中還富裕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.61,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:07.42,Vinland-text,NTP,0,0,0,,要在敵軍趕來之前把這裡洗劫乾淨
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
